formatted_address: 65 Airport Blvd, Transit, Terminal 3, Level 3 Singapore Changi Airport, Singapore 819663
name: dnata Lounge Terminal 3

reviews.text: Small but good selection of foods. Good butter. The meals are very good by airport lounge standards. Professional and attentive, friendly staff. Clean. Nice tea selection. Plenty of electric plug outlets and good WiFi.

Garuda Indonesia Flight is using this lounge for their business or elite pasengger . The location itself is in front of la prairie switzerland high end luxury cream and serum shop . It is very well position signed to reach this loung . They have several seatong area shower and adequate spread of food and drink. It was a pleasant experience .Looking forward to visit again in the next occasion . Please find picture below to see what they offer
Foods gets replenished in a timely manner. Sufficient facility - shower and toilet. Free alcohol :) You need to make your own cocktail, though.

Nice, clean lounge with decent amount of food and drinks. I was there for breakfast and lunch (due to a flight delay) and the food quite decent for both seatings. Good selection of wines, liquor and soft drinks available.
Awesome lounge with great atmosphere. Rraly love the view of the aeroplanes gate near by. Wide range of food available.
